sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant App as React Native App
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as Azure SQL

    U->>App: Navigate to Schedule tab
    App->>API: GET /sessions?week_start=2026-02-23
    API->>DB: SELECT FROM workout_sessions WHERE date BETWEEN
    DB-->>API: Session list
    API-->>App: [{id, title, date, exercises}]
    App->>U: Show workout cards

    U->>App: Tap "Push Day" card
    App->>API: PATCH /sessions/s1 {status: in_progress}
    API->>DB: UPDATE status, started_at
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>App: 200

    App->>API: GET /exercises/last-best?names=[...]
    API->>DB: SELECT exercise_name, MAX(weight_kg) GROUP BY
    DB-->>API: Previous bests
    API-->>App: [{exercise, best_weight, best_reps}]

    App->>U: Active workout screen
    Note over U,App: Voice logging flow<br/>(see Diagram 03)

    U->>App: Tap "Complete Workout"
    App->>API: PATCH /sessions/s1 {status: completed}
    API->>DB: UPDATE status, completed_at
    DB-->>API: OK
    API-->>App: 200
    App->>U: Completion summary
